posting_body: ['Hey there, Jeff here - broker/owner of Rental Fiends - apartment location service.', 'Over the past 15 years I have helped TONS of folks find great places to live.', "I have buildings downtown and nearby with nice 1 beds starting in the 1700's - -", 'I know the market and I know all of the buildings in Denver.', 'Give me a ring and I can help you find a great place to live.', 'There is absolutely no fee to you to use my service - give me a call!', 'show contact info', 'I have apartments all over the downtown area from Rino, to Uptown to Cherry Creek to City Park, Ballpark to Belmar.', 'Thanks!', 'Jeff Settle', 'Broker/Owner', 'Rental Friends', 'show contact info']
